-- Harvard to Play Vanderbilt in First NCAA Tournament Appearance Since 1946
-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 2012-03-11T22:33:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-11/harvard-to-play-vanderbilt-in-first-ncaa-tournament-appearance-since-1946.html
Harvard University  will play
 Vanderbilt University  in its first game in the National
Collegiate Athletic Association men’s basketball tournament
since 1946.  Harvard was named a 12th seed in the East region after
securing its first outright Ivy League championship. Vanderbilt
was named a fifth seed after beating No. 1 Kentucky 71-64 in
today’s Southeastern Conference tournament final.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  